#: chaotic_pfc.dynamics.spectral:3 of
msgid "Power-spectral-density estimation utilities used by the plotting layer."
msgstr ""

#: chaotic_pfc.dynamics.spectral:5 of
msgid ""
"The single public function, :func:`psd_normalised`, wraps "
":func:`scipy.signal.welch` with the conventions adopted throughout the "
"project: peak-normalised magnitude, and the frequency axis expressed as "
"``ω/π ∈ [0, 1]`` rather than cycles or hertz."
msgstr ""

#: ../../api/generated/chaotic_pfc.dynamics.spectral.rst:8
msgid "Functions"
msgstr ""

